data.description: This 4BR, 3BA home is just waiting on your family to move in. This is an Oconee-Capital builder electric. Features include a nice spacious kitchen with a new stove and dishwasher, refrigerator stays, and granite countertops. Eat on bar and a nice dining area. Also includes formal dining, and a great room with an electric fireplace. One bedroom and bath is down. Newer LVP has been installed on the main floor. Upstairs you will find the huge master suite with a sitting area or office space and nice bathroom. Ladies take a look at the master closet too. Also included are two more bedrooms and the 3rd bath. The best feature includes an extra living area or playroom or media room. Newer carpet has also been installed. Exterior features include a screened porch plus a game day fireplace and a privacy fence. Don't let this one get away.
